tooltip_daily_active_users: Number of users who have effective communication every day. Effective communication is defined as one or more question-answer interactions.
tooltip_daily_new_users: Number of new users who have effective communication every day. Effective communication is defined as one or more question-answer interactions.
tooltip_total_messages: Total number of messages generated during user-robot interactions every day.
tooltip_token_consumption: Total tokens consumed by the large model every day, including tokens used for answering questions, optimizing questions, and recommending questions.
